  printf '%s%s\n' "$pad" '⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣴⣙⡽⣯⡝⣋⣡⣴⣤⢿⢡⣿⣿⡿⢊⣤⠾⠋⡩⠂⢀⣴⡫⠕⣊⠕⢁⠔⢁⡼⠋⠁⡁⣸⣿⣿⣿⣿⣛⣿'
